<br>
Nintendo, to my knowledge, isn't as popular as they once were in Japan, and even if the system is great, it'll take some time before it catches up to the PS2 in sales there. <br>
<br>
If any system is going to go the way of the Saturn, it's probably the X-Box. Once again mentioning Japan, I've heard there's very little interest for it there. It's tough for a system to survive if it isn't really popular there.<br>
<br>
Well, it's all a matter of opinion. But those are mine.<br>
